Prove (3.49) p ⋀ (q ≡ r) ≡ p ⋀ r ≡ p ⋀ q ≡ p

  p ⋀ r ≡ p ⋀ q ≡ p
=    〈 golden rule, twice 〉
  p ≡ r ≡ p ⋁ r ≡ p ≡ q ≡ p ⋁ q ≡ p
=    〈 symmetry of ≡, reflexivity of ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ q ≡ p ⋁ r ≡ p ≡ q ≡ r
=    〈 distributivity of ⋁ over ≡ 〉
  p ⋁ (q ≡ r) ≡ p ≡ q ≡ r
=    〈 golden rule 〉
  p ⋀ (q ≡ r)  ╱╱

